title: Court sanctions SEC, orders it to cover legal fees in DEBT Box case
description:
The US Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) has been sanctioned over its disputed restraining order against the crypto firm DEBT Box, according to a March 18 court filing. As a result of the SEC’s misconduct, the court has mandated the commission to cover the legal fees, costs, and expenses incurred by Debt Box. This decision […]
